headline: Agoda unveils four must-visit festival destinations to soak up K-Culture this summer
summary: With summer just around the corner, digital travel platform Agoda highlights four cities—Gangneung, Muju, Buyeo and Tongyeong— where local festivals are drawing increased interest from travelers eager to soak up authentic K-Culture.
